ukudibana ngokupheleleyo: Uthotho olungenasiphelo kuthiwa ludibana ngokupheleleyo ukuba isixa-mali samaxabiso apheleleyo we-sumnds siyaphela.
ixabiso elipheleleyo: Ixabiso elingelona-negative yenani lokwenyani ngaphandle kokujonga uphawu lwalo
uthotho olutshintshanayo: Uluhlu olungenasiphelo olunamagama atshintshanayo phakathi kokulungileyo kunye nokubi
uvavanyo series olutshintshanayo: Indlela esetyenziswayo ukubonisa ukuba uthotho olutshintshanayo olunamagama ahla kwixabiso elipheleleyo luthotho oluguqukayo.
i-annulus: Into emile njengesangqa, ingingqi ebotshelelwe zizangqa ezibini
antiderivative: Umsebenzi owahlulahluko ophuma kuwo ulingana nomsebenzi wokuqala
asymptote: Umgca othi umgama phakathi kwegophe kunye nomgca usondele ku-zero njengenye okanye zombini zika-x okanye u-y zilungelelanisa zithande ukungapheli.
indawo ephantsi kwegophe: Umdibaniso omele indawo ephakathi kwegophe y=f(x), i-x-axis, kunye nemigca ethe nkqo x=a kunye no x=b, apho u-a no-b bayimida yodibaniso.
chain rule: I-derivative ye-composite function yi-derivative yomsebenzi wangaphandle ovavanyiweyo kumaxesha okusebenza angaphakathi i-derivative yomsebenzi wangaphakathi.
icalculus eyahlukileyo: Iphonononga ireyithi yokutshintsha ubungakanani. I-derivative equation isetyenziselwa ukuchaza isantya sotshintsho lomsebenzi
ukuguquguquka okuzimeleyo: Ubungakanani obuguquguqukayo kumsebenzi okanye inxaki, kaninzi imele unobangela kubudlelwane besizathu kunye nesiphumo
ukuguquguquka okuxhomekeke: Isiphumo okanye isiphumo somsebenzi okanye ubudlelwane obutshintshayo ngokusekelwe kumaxabiso obunye ubungakanani
ithambeka: Ibhekisa kuwo onke amaxabiso anokwenzeka anokusetyenziswa njengegalelo kumsebenzi
uluhlu: Iseti yazo zonke iziphumo ezinokwenzeka ukuba umsebenzi unokuvelisa
umda: Ingqikelelo echaza ukuba ngawaphi amaxabiso emveliso umsebenzi osondela kuwo njengoko amagalelo asondela kwixabiso elithile
izinto eziphuma kuyo: Ingqikelelo elinganisa umyinge okhawulezileyo wotshintsho okanye ithambeka lomgca we-tangent kwindawo ethile kumsebenzi.
icalculus ebalulekileyo: Ukongezwa kwekhalculus okubandakanya ukufumana isichasi sokuchasana nomsebenzi okhutshwa ngokuphuma kwawo
umphezulu odityanisiweyo: Ukudityaniswa kwezinto ezidityanisiweyo ezahlukeneyo zokudityaniswa ngaphezulu komphezulu
Izibalo ezininzi: Ukwandiswa kwekhalculus kuguquguquko olunye ukuya kwikhalculus ngemisebenzi yeenguqu ezininzi
icalculus yevektha: Ukongezwa kwekhalculus ejongene nokwahlula kunye nokudityaniswa kwendawo ye-vector kwisithuba se-Euclidean ene-dimensional-ntathu.
iVector enokubakho: Intsimi ye-vector evelisa indawo ye-solenoidal ngokusebenzisa i-curl operator
